net.dempsy.config

Class ClusterId

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dempsy.config.ClusterId

  • public class ClusterId
extends Object

    ClusterIds are a unique Id of a message processor Cluster within a Dempsy application. Cluster Id's are essentially a two level unique name made up by the application name and a cluster name.

    ClusterIds are immutable.
